StringTable Class Reference

This class contains all string that might be written in the MapCentral system. More...

#include <StringTable.h>

[legend]
Collaboration diagram for StringTable:

List of all members.

Countries.

The countries that are available.

Used for storage in the maps. To get a (printable) string with the name of the country, methods in this class must be used! The extension "_CC" is for CountryCode.

Detailed Description

This class contains all string that might be written in the MapCentral system.

All functions are static.

Method to be used when printing routedescription that contains the exit count.

E.g. "Take the 2:nd street to the left".

Parameters:
sc The stringcode that describes the turn.
cc In what language we want the string.
